					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-636334#post-1756247</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-636334/letters-to-a-prophet#post-1756247</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2013 16:55:29 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>1324229</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>It might as well be farsi for all the meaning I've extracted.</p> </blockquote> <p>I probably would have understood it better had it been in Persian, honestly.</p> <p>I actually found this really grating. Intentionally obnoxious is still obnoxious, and the internet is chock full of people whose schtick is &quot;I'm-so-self-absorbed-and-awesome-except-that's-my-persona-kind-of,&quot; and references to various GoI things didn't make this any more bearable.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
